name: The Cab - Poster Set
description:
We are selling all of these items in order to raise money for our friend Dom. She has recently been diagnosed with Hodgkin's Lymphoma. We are hoping to raise funds in order to help her pay for treatment. 100% of the money raised will be given directly to Dom. Please help this cause.

All items are being donated by Cash Colligan, former bassist of The Cab.

This set comes with Posters, pins, buttons and Stickers from The Cab.

There are only 15 Left - First Come First Served

*We are sorry for the expensive shipping costs, but this is a fundraiser. Thank you very much for your support!
